g"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023003034632865688"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1vaI/+rz2dk/EAMaCTExODk5Mzk5MSDFzLfOBjAAOEFAGnITMjAyMzAwMzAzNDYzMjg2NTY4OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1775200215.51212", "card_id": "Q_2019834289672435071", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国内三大编程模型（Kimi K2.5, GLM 5, Minimax M2.7）我应该选择哪个？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本人大一工科学生，想在课余时间尝试 AI 编程。 编程软件：Opencode+oh my opencode。 听说 Kimi 最强，但是相对价格较高（50CNY/mo）；而 Minimax 最便宜（30CNY/mo）但是由于参数量小性能较差。 参考价格与性能，我应该选择什么模型；或者说，在这个价格区间，价格根本不是需要考虑的问题"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6002e9e5bbe03509aab4242b2bc35b3b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019834289672435071"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI1vaI/+rz2dk/EAMaCTExODg4MzExMSClvonOBjAAOP0BQBtyEzIwMTk4MzQyODk2NzI0MzUwNzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1775200215.52081", "card_id": "Q_2020063029404938744", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 298}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "老丈人每年都回老家上坟 2 次，每次都需要车接车送，来回 1500 公里，怎么劝都劝不住，我该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "背景：我们两口子都是普通上班族，媳妇家只剩下老丈人一人 70 多岁了，我这边也只有我母亲也 70 多了。老丈人之前脑梗过，担心老人身体，给接到身边一起生活。一人上班没办法养家，把我母亲也叫到帮忙带孩子，小孩刚上幼儿园。我也考虑过让老丈人给带孩子，但是老人不会做饭，再加上老丈人身体不好所以给老母亲也叫来了。担心俩老人不好相处给老丈人单独租的房子住的（租金 + 水电物业每月 1500）。平时生活很和谐大家小家有劲一块使，虽然过得不富裕，但还是很快乐。 老丈人老家是济宁的对于上坟这个事观念特别深，每年清明还有十月一都必须回家上坟，媳妇多次劝说都不行，坚持回家。每年清明回家时还想着在家里小住一段时间，每年就得 3 个来回，一次来回加上过路费油费走亲戚费用就得 2000，我俩口就是普通收入真心感觉压力大。我还不好说什么，媳妇也说不动老人。也想过让老人清明回家，等着十一上完坟再接回来，但又担心老丈人身体（毕竟 3 年前脑梗过），大家有没有好的解决办法"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3ddc5f3df9fdfa6f1fa042d566654c47.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2020063029404938744"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI1vaI/+rz2dk/EAMaCTExODg4OTE2OCCt6IzOBjAAOPgEQBxyEzIwMjAwNjMwMjk0MDQ5Mzg3NDR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1775200215.52998", "card_id": "Q_2014740208004924096", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在数学研究中，找到「解」的瞬间是一种怎样的感受？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在数学的世界里，最迷人的时刻或许不是大功告成的 Q.E.D，而是逻辑碎片在脑海中瞬间对齐的刹那。 这种感受被阿基米德描述为「Eureka!」，被辛格形容为「一种几乎带有痛感的清晰」。它可能发生在长达数月的苦思冥想后，也可能诞生于一个平凡午后的神来之笔。 诚邀各位热爱数学的只有来分享那个瞬间的感受。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-49d4c9ad19793598cfd2f5f1736daf51_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014740208004924096"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1vaI/+rz2dk/EAMaCTExODcwMjQwNyDprb/NBjAAOGtAHXITMjAxNDc0MDIwODAwNDkyNDA5NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "